    <title>Hexo使用指南</title>
    <link href="http://freaty.github.io/2025/08/20/Hexo/"/>
    <id>http://freaty.github.io/2025/08/20/Hexo/</id>
    <published>2025-08-19T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-08-19T16:00:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-Hexo-初步安装与部署"><a href="#1-Hexo-初步安装与部署" class="headerlink" title="1 Hexo 初步安装与部署"></a>1 Hexo 初步安装与部署</h2><h3 id="1-1-环境准备"><a href="#1-1-环境准备" class="headerlink" title="1.1 环境准备"></a>1.1 环境准备</h3><h4 id="1-1-1-安装-Node-js"><a href="#1-1-1-安装-Node-js" class="headerlink" title="1.1.1 安装 Node.js"></a>1.1.1 安装 Node.js</h4><p>Hexo 基于 Node.js 运行，需先安装 Node.js（建议使用LTS版本）：</p><ul><li>  安装命令：<a href="https://nodejs.org/">Node.js 官网</a></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Windows安装LTS版本命令，也可官网下载安装</span></span><br><span class="line">winget install OpenJS.NodeJS.LTS</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Linux安装最新22LTS版本命令，不同发行版包管理工具不同，debian系为apt</span></span><br><span class="line">curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_22.x | <span class="built_in">sudo</span> -E bash -</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install nodejs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>  验证配置：</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 验证安装</span></span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 配置设定，以Linux为例，Windows一般无需配置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将默认的系统级路径改为用户主目录下的.npm-global</span></span><br><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> prefix ~/.npm-global</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将新的npm全局二进制文件目录添加到环境变量PATH中</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;export PATH=~/.npm-global/bin:$PATH&#x27;</span> &gt;&gt; ~/.bashrc</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-1-2-安装-Git"><a href="#1-1-2-安装-Git" class="headerlink" title="1.1.2 安装 Git"></a>1.1.2 安装 Git</h4><p>用于版本控制和部署到 GitHub 等平台：</p><ul><li>  安装命令：<a href="https://git-scm.com/">Git 官网</a></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Windows安装命令，也可官网下载安装</span></span><br><span class="line">winget install git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Linux安装命令，不同发行版包管理工具不同，debian系为apt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>  验证配置：</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 验证安装</span></span><br><span class="line">git --version  <span class="comment"># 输出版本号</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 配置Git</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">&quot;Your Name&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">&quot;your_email@example.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># SSH密钥生成</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C <span class="string">&quot;your_email@example.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 复制公钥添加到Github等平台账户相应设置内</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cat</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-2-安装-Hexo"><a href="#1-2-安装-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="1.2 安装 Hexo"></a>1.2 安装 Hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 全局安装Hexo命令</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 验证Hexo命令</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3-初始化-Hexo-博客"><a href="#1-3-初始化-Hexo-博客" class="headerlink" title="1.3.初始化 Hexo 博客"></a>1.3.初始化 Hexo 博客</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 新建文件夹（名称自定义，如 my-hexo-blog）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> my-hexo-blog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入博客目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> my-hexo-blog</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 初始化项目</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装依赖包</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>初始化后生成的核心目录：</p><ul><li>  <code>source/</code>：存放博客文章与资源（<code>.md</code> 文件和依赖的资源）</li><li>  <code>themes/</code>：主题文件夹</li><li>  <code>_config.yml</code>：Hexo 全局配置文件</li><li>  <code>package.json</code>：项目依赖配置</li></ul><h3 id="1-4-本地预览博客"><a href="#1-4-本地预览博客" class="headerlink" title="1.4 本地预览博客"></a>1.4 本地预览博客</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 生成静态文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo generate  <span class="comment"># 简写：hexo g</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 启动本地服务器</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo server    <span class="comment"># 简写：hexo s</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打开浏览器，访问 http://localhost:4000 即可查看本地博客</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-5-发布第一篇文章"><a href="#1-5-发布第一篇文章" class="headerlink" title="1.5 发布第一篇文章"></a>1.5 发布第一篇文章</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建新文章（简写：hexo n &quot;标题&quot;）</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new <span class="string">&quot;Hexo&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 编辑文章（这里示例用vscode编辑.md文件）</span></span><br><span class="line">code <span class="built_in">source</span>/_posts/Hexo.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重新本地预览</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-6-安装主题（以-Maupassant-为例）"><a href="#1-6-安装主题（以-Maupassant-为例）" class="headerlink" title="1.6 安装主题（以 Maupassant 为例）"></a>1.6 安装主题（以 Maupassant 为例）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下载主题到主题目录</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/tufu9441/maupassant-hexo.git themes/maupassant</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 阅读Maupassant主题Github说明页面并依照说明配置依赖和个性化设置</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 修改Hexo全局配置文件 _config.yml 的theme: 为maupassant</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-7-部署到-GitHub-Pages"><a href="#1-7-部署到-GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="1.7 部署到 GitHub Pages"></a>1.7 部署到 GitHub Pages</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装部署插件</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在全局 _config.yml 中添加：（非终端命令，为配置文件添加插件设置）</span></span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 特别强调你的GitHub仓库名称必需为：你的用户名.github.io</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: git@github.com:你的用户名/你的用户名.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: main  <span class="comment"># 部署分支（默认 main 或 master）</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 部署到 GitHub Pages</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g -d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 部署成功后，访问 https://你的用户名.github.io即可查看线上博客</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-Markdown-知识"><a href="#2-Markdown-知识" class="headerlink" title="2 Markdown 知识"></a>2 Markdown 知识</h2><h3 id="2-1-页面属性配置"><a href="#2-1-页面属性配置" class="headerlink" title="2.1 页面属性配置"></a>2.1 页面属性配置</h3><h4 id="2-1-1-基础布局属性"><a href="#2-1-1-基础布局属性" class="headerlink" title="2.1.1 基础布局属性"></a>2.1.1 基础布局属性</h4><ul><li>1 <code>layout</code><ul><li>作用：指定页面 &#x2F; 文章的渲染模板，决定页面结构和功能。</li><li>常用值（Maupassant 主题支持）：<ul><li><code>post</code>：默认，博客文章（支持分类、标签等）。</li><li><code>page</code>：独立页面（如 “关于页”，带侧边栏）。</li><li><code>tagcloud</code>：标签云页面（展示所有标签及权重）。</li><li><code>single-column</code>：单栏页面（无侧边栏）。</li><li><code>blogroll</code>：友链页面（展示友情链接，需配合主题配置的<code>links</code>）。</li><li><code>timeline</code>：时间线页面（展示网站历史，需配合主题配置的<code>timeline</code>）。</li></ul></li></ul></li><li>2 <code>title</code><ul><li>作用：定义文章 &#x2F; 页面标题，显示在页面头部、浏览器标签及搜索结果中。</li></ul></li><li>3 <code>date</code><ul><li>作用：设置发布时间，用于文章排序和展示（如 “发布于 2024-01-01”）。</li><li>格式：<code>YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS</code>（时间可选）。</li></ul></li><li>4 <code>updated</code><ul><li>作用：设置最后更新时间，用于展示 “最后编辑于 XXX”。</li></ul></li><li>5 <code>permalink</code><ul><li>作用：自定义永久链接（URL），覆盖 Hexo 默认规则（如<code>year/month/day/title/</code>）。</li></ul></li><li>6 <code>published</code><ul><li>作用：控制是否发布。<code>true</code>（默认）发布，<code>false</code>为本地草稿（不生成静态文件）。</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="2-1-2-分类标签属性"><a href="#2-1-2-分类标签属性" class="headerlink" title="2.1.2 分类标签属性"></a>2.1.2 分类标签属性</h4><ul><li>1 <code>categories</code><ul><li>作用：指定文章分类（支持单分类或多级分类）。</li></ul></li><li>2 <code>tags</code><ul><li>作用：指定文章标签（关联相似内容），支持多个标签。</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="2-1-3-内容展示属性"><a href="#2-1-3-内容展示属性" class="headerlink" title="2.1.3 内容展示属性"></a>2.1.3 内容展示属性</h4><ul><li>1 <code>description</code><ul><li>作用：定义文章摘要，用于首页 &#x2F; 列表页展示（替代<code>&lt;!--more--&gt;</code>）。</li></ul></li><li>2 <code>toc</code><ul><li>作用：控制是否显示目录（Table of Contents）。</li></ul></li><li>3 <code>excerpt</code><ul><li>作用：手动定义摘要，功能同<code>description</code>。</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="2-1-4-功能控制属性"><a href="#2-1-4-功能控制属性" class="headerlink" title="2.1.4 功能控制属性"></a>2.1.4 功能控制属性</h4><ul><li>1 <code>comments</code><ul><li>作用：控制是否启用评论功能（覆盖全局配置，true&#x2F;false）。</li></ul></li><li>2 <code>mathjax</code> &#x2F; <code>mathjax2</code><ul><li>作用：启用数学公式渲染（需先在 Hexo 全局配置<code>_config.yml</code>中开启对应选项）。</li></ul></li><li>3 <code>donate</code><ul><li>作用：控制当前页面是否显示捐赠按钮（覆盖主题全局配置）。</li></ul></li><li>4 <code>sticky</code><ul><li>作用：设置文章置顶权重（数值越大，优先级越高）。</li></ul></li><li>5 <code>password</code><ul><li>作用：对文章设置密码保护，访问时需输入密码查看内容。</li></ul></li><li>6 <code>abbrlink</code><ul><li>作用：生成短链接（需配合<code>hexo-abbrlink</code>插件），替代默认长链接。</li></ul></li></ul><p><img src="/images/Hexo.jpeg" alt="Hexo"></p>]]></content>
    
    
